@NODE "REGISTRY"     "How to register, or contact Trebor!"

     If you do not register this Tool, you will not be able to send OLM`s
     in the program.  Registration is completely !FREE!.
     This tool is Mail-Ware, if you wish to register this Professional tool
     then all you have to do is write EMail or Snail Mail to me at the 
     following addresses.

     trebor@funhouse.thenet.co.uk   [ Internet EMail ]
     trebor@2:2502/24.0             [  FidoNet Mail  ]

     Robert Hewick             	    [  Home address! ]
     30 George Street,              [  Feel free to  ]
     Hedon, Hull,                   [ send donations ]
